articles.title: IND A vs Pak A Highlights, Emerging Asia Cup 2023 Final: Pakistan A Beat India A By 128 Runs To Retain Title - NDTV Sports
articles.description: IND A vs Pak A Final Highlights: Fiery century by Tayyab Tahir, followed by a three-wicket haul from Sufiyan Muqeem guided Pakistan A to a massive 128-run victory over India A in the Emerging Asia Cup 2023 final on Sunday in Colombo.
